⍝ ZBus.Nats Core NATS test suite
⍝ Validates: headers, describe, queue groups, multiple subs, close cascade
⍝ Requires nats-server running on localhost:4222

⎕IO ⎕ML←1
pass←1
tests←0 ⋄ passed←0

dll←'D:\devel\Z-Format\src\ZBus.Nats\bin\Release\net10.0\win-x64\publish\ZBus.Nats.dll'

⍝ ── Define ⎕NA bindings ──────────────────────────────────────────────

'zbus_init'         ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_init <0T1 >Z'
'zbus_wait'         ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_wait& <0T1 I4 >Z >Z >Z'
'zbus_close'        ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_close <0T1'
'zbus_exists'       ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_exists <0T1'
'zbus_names'        ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_names <0T1 >Z'
'zbus_describe'     ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_describe <0T1 >Z'
'zbus_getprop'      ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_getprop <0T1 <0T1 >Z'
'nats_connect'      ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_nats_connect <0T1 <0T1'
'nats_pub'          ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_nats_pub <0T1 <0T1 <Z'
'nats_sub'          ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_nats_sub <0T1 <0T1 =Z'

⍝ ── Helpers ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

check←{
    tests+←1
    rc evt expected←⍵
    :If evt≡expected
        passed+←1
        ⎕←'  ✓ ',⍺
    :Else
        pass←0
        ⎕←'  ✗ ',⍺,' (expected "',expected,'", got "',evt,'")'
    :EndIf
}

⍝ ── Setup ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

⎕←'══════════════════════════════════════════'
⎕←' ZBus.Nats Core Test Suite'
⎕←'══════════════════════════════════════════'
⎕←''

(rc rootName)←zbus_init 'C1' 0
:If rc≠0 ⋄ ⎕←'FATAL: init failed' ⋄ ⎕OFF 1 ⋄ :EndIf
rc←nats_connect 'C1' 'nats://localhost:4222'
:If rc≠0 ⋄ ⎕←'FATAL: connect failed' ⋄ ⎕OFF 1 ⋄ :EndIf
(rc obj evt data)←zbus_wait 'C1' 5000 0 0 0
:If evt≢'Connected' ⋄ ⎕←'FATAL: not connected (',evt,')' ⋄ ⎕OFF 1 ⋄ :EndIf

⎕←'Connected to NATS'
⎕←''

⍝ ── Test: Describe root ──────────────────────────────────────────────

⎕←'Test: Describe root'
tests+←1
(rc info)←zbus_describe 'C1' 0
:If rc=0
    ⎕←'  [1]=',1⊃info
    ⎕←'  [2]=',2⊃info
    ⎕←'  [3]=',3⊃info
    ⎕←'  [4]=',4⊃info
    :If (1⊃info)≡'[ZBus.Nats]'
        passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ root describe returns adapter metadata'
    :Else
        pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ unexpected [1]: ',1⊃info
    :EndIf
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ describe failed rc=',⍕rc
:EndIf

⍝ ── Test: Publish with headers ──────────────────────────────────────

⎕←''
⎕←'Test: Publish with headers'
(rc subName)←nats_sub 'C1' 'hdrsub' 'test.hdrs'
:If rc≠0 ⋄ pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ subscribe failed' ⋄ :EndIf

⍝ Build headers: 2×2 matrix (key, value per row)
hdrs←2 2⍴'X-Source' 'APL' 'X-Version' '1.0'
payload←'payload with headers'

⍝ Publish with (payload, headers) nested pair
rc←nats_pub 'C1' 'test.hdrs' (payload hdrs)
tests+←1
:If rc=0
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ publish with headers rc=0'
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ publish failed rc=',⍕rc
:EndIf

⍝ Receive and check headers in event data
(rc obj evt data)←zbus_wait 'C1' 5000 0 0 0
tests+←1
:If evt≡'Msg'
    ⍝ data is (subject, replyTo, payload, headers)
    msgSubj←1⊃data
    msgPayload←3⊃data
    msgHdrs←4⊃data
    ⎕←'  received subject=',msgSubj
    ⎕←'  headers shape=',(⍕⍴msgHdrs)
    :If 2=⍴⍴msgHdrs
        passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ headers received as matrix'
    :Else
        pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ expected 2D headers, got shape ',(⍕⍴msgHdrs)
    :EndIf
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ expected Msg, got ',evt
:EndIf

⍝ ── Test: Multiple subscriptions ────────────────────────────────────

⎕←''
⎕←'Test: Multiple subscriptions'
(rc sub1)←nats_sub 'C1' 'sub1' 'multi.>'
(rc2 sub2)←nats_sub 'C1' 'sub2' 'multi.>'
tests+←1
:If (rc=0)∧(rc2=0)
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ two subs created: ',sub1,' and ',sub2
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ sub creation failed'
:EndIf

⍝ Publish — both should receive
rc←nats_pub 'C1' 'multi.test' 'both get this'
(rc obj1 evt1 d1)←zbus_wait 'C1' 3000 0 0 0
(rc obj2 evt2 d2)←zbus_wait 'C1' 3000 0 0 0
tests+←1
:If (evt1≡'Msg')∧(evt2≡'Msg')
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ both subs received: ',obj1,' and ',obj2
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ not both received: ',evt1,' ',evt2
:EndIf

⍝ ── Test: Describe subscription ─────────────────────────────────────

⎕←''
⎕←'Test: Describe subscription'
(rc info)←zbus_describe sub1 0
tests+←1
:If rc=0
    ⎕←'  [1]=',1⊃info
    ⎕←'  [2]=',2⊃info
    ⎕←'  [3]=',3⊃info
    ⎕←'  [4]=',4⊃info
    :If (2⊃info)≡'Subscription'
        passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ subscription describe works'
    :Else
        pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ unexpected type'
    :EndIf
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ describe failed rc=',⍕rc
:EndIf

⍝ ── Test: Close subscription (cascade) ──────────────────────────────

⎕←''
⎕←'Test: Close subscription'
rc←zbus_close ⊂sub1
tests+←1
:If rc=0
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ close sub1 rc=0'
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ close failed rc=',⍕rc
:EndIf

⍝ Verify it no longer exists
rc←zbus_exists ⊂sub1
tests+←1
:If rc≠0
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ sub1 no longer exists'
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ sub1 still exists after close'
:EndIf

⍝ sub2 should still work — but first drain the synthetic Closed event for sub1
(rc obj evt data)←zbus_wait 'C1' 1000 0 0 0
:If evt≡'Closed' ⋄ ⎕←'  (drained Closed event for ',obj,')' ⋄ :EndIf

rc←nats_pub 'C1' 'multi.alive' 'still here'
(rc obj evt data)←zbus_wait 'C1' 3000 0 0 0
tests+←1
:If (evt≡'Msg')∧(obj≡sub2)
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ sub2 still active after sub1 closed'
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ sub2 state unexpected: evt=',evt,' obj=',obj
:EndIf

⍝ ── Test: GetProperty ────────────────────────────────────────────────

⎕←''
⎕←'Test: GetProperty'
(rc val)←zbus_getprop 'C1' 'State' 0
tests+←1
:If (rc=0)∧(val≡'Connected')
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ State=Connected'
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ State property: rc=',(⍕rc),' val=',val
:EndIf

(rc val)←zbus_getprop 'C1' 'Url' 0
tests+←1
:If (rc=0)∧(val≡'nats://localhost:4222')
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ Url=nats://localhost:4222'
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ Url property: rc=',(⍕rc),' val=',val
:EndIf

⍝ ── Cleanup ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

⎕←''
rc←zbus_close ⊂'C1'

⎕←'══════════════════════════════════════════'
⎕←' Results: ',(⍕passed),'/',(⍕tests),' passed'
:If pass
    ⎕←' ═══ ALL CORE TESTS PASSED ═══'
:Else
    ⎕←' *** SOME TESTS FAILED ***'
:EndIf
⎕←'══════════════════════════════════════════'
